comments[3]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-01T11:57:17.043Z",cursor-agent,Created after list-open/list-in-progress/list-blocked plus terminal-focused search showed no duplicate item for this scope.
  "2026-04-01T18:53:10.935Z",cursor-agent,"Follow-up continuation of this existing terminal epic (no duplicate item created). Reproduced residual behavior on 2026-04-01: pm test-all --status in_progress --timeout 60 --json remained silent for about 170s before final output/exit while linked tests were active. Acceptance delta for reopen: spawn-based linked-test orchestration, default stderr heartbeat/progress, and deterministic timeout tree termination across PTY environments."
  "2026-04-01T19:10:50.178Z",cursor-agent,"Reproduced and validated PTY reliability follow-up end to end: script -q -c \"pm test-all --status in_progress --timeout 60 --json\" /tmp/pm-test-all-pty.log now shows continuous [pm test] linked-test heartbeat progress lines and deterministic completion payload instead of long silent intervals. Full regression remains green (node scripts/run-tests.mjs test: 693/693)."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-01T11:57:17.043Z",cursor-agent,"Implement in phased streams: stdin fail-safe,graceful exits,subprocess anti-hang,regression tests,docs parity."
